<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="302" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1267,1582]" pageId="1" pageNumber="302">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1519,1545]" pageId="1" pageNumber="302">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species was reported from mangroves, mangrove associated areas, and brackish water areas. Scanning electron microscopic observations of this species from Goa were given in Chatterjee 
<emphasis box="[1214,1263,1555,1581]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="302">et al</emphasis>
. (2013).
</paragraph>
